Required attribution string
---------------------------
This integration emits the following attribution on every sensor (via the
`attribution` state attribute) and in every diagnostics download:

    Datenquelle: E-Control

If you build a Lovelace card or any other user-facing UI on top of this
integration, please keep this attribution visible.

